text: Chulpan () is a rural locality (a village) in Yangatausky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 376 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Maloyaz, 3 km from Yangatau. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Chulpan, Salavatsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
